title: You Know You Like It: Tootie's August 2015 Mix
description:
August is here, and that means a wedding, Team Kobashi vs. Team Tootie softball (maybe) and the Slip-N-Fly Music Festival are all around the corner. Does that mean anything in the context of this mix? Not really, though some of the wedding requests were used in this mix, and some tracks are here only because of other related wedding requests. Whatever. Enjoy.

The method focuses on vocal volume.
